est-gaming-mouse-140004638.html">最佳游戏鼠标</a>指南中的首选预算选择。侧面有几个可自定义的按钮，整体形状应该适合右撇子和左撇子。它的尺寸当然较小，滚轮有点软，橡胶电缆也不是超级灵活，但对于 20 美元来说，很难做得更好了。</p><h2> HyperX Cloud Alpha 无线</h2><p><core-commerce id="58107f4d75f64435a1d6cc70a6ae68c0" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:57;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9ncC9wcm9kdWN0L0IwOVRSVzU3V0I_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMXM2LTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJkN2M2ZjUxMS05ZmQ2LTQzNGUtYjUwZi00ZTQ1NDk3YmNhYTMifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAXLqBcdYeHppyJEJVrlMEue2kyGfd6P0Gi0g9Xcf2z0r&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB09TRW57WB" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B09TRW57WB?th=1" class="rapid-with-clickid">HyperX Cloud Alpha Wireless</a>在亚马逊的售价降至 152 美元，比近几个月的平均市场价格低约 30 美元。如果亚马逊库存告罄， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Best Buy;elmt:;cpos:58;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=5e0bed65-d2f8-4b34-9b8f-955218c0e37a&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Best+Buy&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAcd4ngGIGYN0a-pheMHVRNBSDPzbI7FI1eh3malQ5xsp&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bestbuy.com%2Fsite%2Fhyperx-cloud-alpha-wireless-dts-headphonex-gaming-headset-for-pc-ps5-and-ps4-black%2F6499569.p%3FskuId%3D6499569" class="rapid-with-clickid">百思买</a>可以加价 2 美元购买。 Cloud Alpha Wireless 是我们<a data-i13n="cpos:59;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-gaming-headset-130006477.html">最佳游戏耳机</a>指南中的首选无线耳机，主要是因为其惊人的电池寿命，一次充电可持续使用 300 多个小时。它的麦克风和低音重的声音配置几乎没有同类领先，但它们很好，而且整个设备一次佩戴几个小时都很舒适。最大的问题是，您不应该为 HyperX 的配套软件所困扰，因为有<a data-i13n="cpos:60;pos:1" href="https://xander51.medium.com/