标价下降了 20 美元。</p><p> Air Pro 3 是我们<a data-i13n="cpos:67;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-budget-wireless-earbuds-130028735.html#runnerupearfunairpro3">最佳预算无线耳机</a>指南中的亚军。它具有与我们的首选<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:68;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAX1GTbmeMcOWQHW9GdAsJi0MbMAoKA_5Q4FHTY1U12EN&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fsoundcore-Adaptive-Cancelling-Comfortable-Customization%2Fdp%2FB0B1LVC5VZ%2F" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/soundcore-Adaptive-Cancelling-Comfortable-Customization/dp/B0B1LVC5VZ/?th=1" class="rapid-with-clickid">Soundcore Space A40</a>类似的功能集，具有可用的主动降噪功能、支持无线充电和多点连接、IPX5 防水性和稳定的贴合性。虽然它令人兴奋的声音并不适合所有人，但它确实为嘻哈和电子音乐提供了强烈的低音响应。它的电池续航时间和 ANC 不如 Space A40 那么令人印象深刻，但如果你想节省一些现金或只是喜欢 AirPods 风格的“杆”设计，它是一个强有力的选择。</p><h2>没有什么耳棒</h2><p><core-commerce id="965c3fd5569246c39e0a0c6e93ef5d19" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;cpos:69;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3VzLm5vdGhpbmcudGVjaC9wcm9kdWN0cy9lYXItc3RpY2siLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImQ3YzZmNTExLTlmZDYtNDM0ZS1iNTBmLTRlNDU0OTdiY2FhMyJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAXccpNemaFJNEiCd91Qo4XHjV__RPXnwnO0qkAbpp8QS&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fus.nothing.tech%2Fproducts%2Fear-stick" class="rapid-with-clickid">Nothing Ear Stick</a>在同一指南中获得了<a data-i13n="cpos:70;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-budget-wireless-earbuds-130028735.html#honorablementions">荣誉奖</a>，现在在 Nothing 的在线商店中售价降至 79 美元。对于本质上缺乏深沉低音的开放式耳塞来说，这仍然有点贵，但比平常便宜了 20 美元。</p><p>我们向那些讨厌真正入耳式耳机感觉的人推荐耳棒，因为这种开放式设计位于外耳上，而不是一直进入耳道。虽然 50 美元的<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:71;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAATfRT1BuMdEnY4g0ETExhgwLD1VZ_qkjHfVvcusel58C&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FAll-new-Echo-Buds-2023-Release-True-Wireless-Earbuds%2Fdp%2FB09JVG3TWX%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">亚马逊 Echo Buds</a>整体价值更高，但 Ear Stick 的设计更时尚，透明的外壳可以像口红管一样旋转打开。对于这种风格的耳塞来说，其音频质量非常稳定（并且可以根据需要进行定制），而 AirPods 风格的触摸控制则易于使用。每次充电 6 小时左右，电池续航时间还过得去。请记住，这种类型的设计几乎无法阻挡外界噪音，因此它不适合飞行或拥挤的办公室。</p><h2>苹果航空标签</h2><p><core-commerce id="a8bf8d02852f4d2fa1a0749e448e49f1" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:72;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAZ15PBFyMKoCK-eTkyUolU147qP72NYQx9kVJUFsk6f-&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FApple-MX532AM-A-AirTag%2Fdp%2FB0933BVK6T%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">Apple AirTag</a>在<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:73;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAZ15PBFyMKoCK-eTkyUolU147qP72NYQx9kVJUFsk6f-&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FApple-MX532AM-A-AirTag%2Fdp%2FB0933BVK6T%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">亚马逊</a>和<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Walmart;elmt:;cpos:74;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=3719d8d4-5edd-4817-998a-91f3229e7323&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Walmart&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiIzNzE5ZDhkNC01ZWRkLTQ4MTctOTk4YS05MWYzMjI5ZTczMjMiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly